<div class="pages">
  <h1>About Minnesota Reflections</h1>
  <p><strong>Minnesota Reflections</strong> is a database of digitized original materials shared by cultural heritage organizations located across our state. These materials include images, text, audio, film, and more, with new items added on a regular basis. The resources found on this site support research for scholars, educators, students, and the public. Minnesota Reflections is the premier project of the <a href="http://mndigital.org/">Minnesota Digital Library</a>.</p>
